
# Chat Room

Simple real-time chat app using Node.js, Express, and Socket.IO.  
Users join a room with a code and chat with each other.

## How to run

### 1. Clone the repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/SaiKumar2121/chat-room.git
cd chat-room
```

### 2. Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Start the server

```bash
node server.js
```

### 4. Open in browser

Go to:

```
http://localhost:3000
```
